contentrichtext.text: '''Houghton Lake''' may refer to: * [[Houghton Lake, Michigan]], an unincorporated community * [[Houghton Lake (Michigan)]], in Roscommon County, Michigan, the largest inland lake in the state * [[Houghton Lake (Ogemaw County, Michigan)]], a small lake in Cumming Township, Ogemaw County, Michigan * [[Houghton Lake, (Indiana)]], a small lake in [[Marshall County, Indiana]] * [[Houghton Lake (Saskatchewan)]], a lake in the [[Lenore Lake (Saskatchewan)]] basin == See also == * [[Houghton Lake Heights, Michigan]] {{geodis}}
